---
  title: About
---

<div class="page-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-lg-10 col-xl-8">
        <h2 class="page-section__heading text-center">
          <span>About Me</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="page-section__lead text-center">
          I'm a dad. I'm a husband. I'm a New Hampshire native with a Colorado problem. The first album I owned was Blondie's <i>Autoamerican</i>. I recently put on two different shoes, walked around an apple orchard, and failed to notice. 
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<div class="page-section mb-5">
  <div class="container-fluid" style="max-width: 1600px;">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col align-self-center d-none d-sm-block d-md-block d-lg-block">
        <%= image_tag('about/about1.jpg', :class => 'img-fluid') %>
      </div>
      <div class="col align-self-start d-none d-lg-block">
        <%= image_tag('about/about2.jpg', :class => 'img-fluid') %>
      </div>
      <div class="col align-self-end pt-lg-5">
        <%= image_tag('about/about3.jpg', :class => 'img-fluid') %>
      </div>
      <div class="col align-self-center d-none d-xl-block">
        <%= image_tag('about/about4.jpg', :class => 'img-fluid') %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="page-section page-section--gray">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-lg-10 col-xl-8">
        <h2 class="page-section__heading text-center">
          <span>Trails</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="page-section__lead text-center">
          I maintain the Hurricane Trail <span style="font-style:italic;font-family:baskerville,serif;">&amp;</span> Asquam-Ridge Trail, two of my favorites on Mount Moosilauke. I'm often joined by family and friends, making the work and mood even lighter.
